--ques.2) write aquery to retrieve all the orders placed in the last 30 days for
a specific user.

```sql
-- Table: orders
-- Columns: orderid,userid,dishname, orderdate,amount
```


---solution 02.)

select dishname , sum(amount) as total_orders
from orders
where userid='u123' and orderdate>=date_sub(curdate(),interval 30 days);





















